Bxc6
{ Surprisingly, this is actually meant to be more critical. Again, you just sort of have to believe me. }
8... bxc6 9. Nxc6 Qe8
{ I played 9...Qd5?? in a blitz game once. I wouldn't recommend repeating that. }
10. Nxe7+ Qxe7
{ Now, the Light Squares around White's King are a bit weak, but he can also pick up the c4 pawn  (and be up a pawn)  pretty much at will. }
