{ Good move - avoiding the Queen trade and setting up the threat of ...Ng4. Notice how Black is getting mobilized before White has had a chance to unfreeze his Queenside. }
16. f3 Bc4 { Another good move - threatening ...Re8 and taking on e2. } 17. Nc3
