17... Qe6 { Good move - no need to rush. } 18. Nc3 Ne4 19. Nxe4 Qxe4
{ Followed by taking on e2, with no problems, as in Loeschnauer-Gilbert, correspondence 2016. 20 Be3 and 20 e3 both lose to Bh3. }
