Rb8 9. Qa4 Nb4 10. Qxa7 Bd7 11. Ne5 Nfd5
{ This has been tried most often, but it allows White a bail-out tactic. } 12.
Qxb8 Qxb8 13. Nxd7 Qa7 14. Nxf8 Bxf8
{ White has two Rooks for the Queen, and is arguably a bit better. This isn't horrible for Black, but it's not great compared to what he had previously. }
