1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. g3 d5 4. Bg2 Be7 5. Nf3 O-O 6. cxd5
{ Before I conclude, I just thought I'd mention that this exchange generally doesn't favour White - after ...c6, the "Catalan Bishop" tends to bite on granite, while the c8 Bishop's diagonal has been opened. }
6... exd5 7. O-O c6 8. Nc3 Bf5 { ...with a good game for Black. } *

